{"id": "ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_VERY_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 236, "displayName": {"text": "Nisei", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVemJ6RnNUbUZaUm5WUFdGOUNUM3A2Vm0xQ1JuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "Posting this review late, but I still wanted to share my experience. For me, the value was not very high for the price. Some dishes were a bit strange and were described very highly by the staff, but did not really meet expectations. There were also some charges that were not clearly explained to us in advance. During the menu introduction, the service felt a little unprepared and at times they even forgot how to describe certain dishes.\n\nThat being said, some dishes were quite tasty and the seasonal ingredients tasted fresh. However, in my opinion, this was not the best standard I would expect from a Michelin one star restaurant. I hope they continue to improve.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Posting this review late, but I still wanted to share my experience. For me, the value was not very high for the price. Some dishes were a bit strange and were described very highly by the staff, but did not really meet expectations. There were also some charges that were not clearly explained to us in advance. During the menu introduction, the service felt a little unprepared and at times they even forgot how to describe certain dishes.\n\nThat being said, some dishes were quite tasty and the seasonal ingredients tasted fresh. However, in my opinion, this was not the best standard I would expect from a Michelin one star restaurant. I hope they continue to improve.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "QQ", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115400097618155865225/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVScep8UFALSlc81J8dgbvZUNefQBjk93qvwE0STwrsNSihwdAS=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T03:31:24.827380852Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVemJ6RnNUbUZaUm5WUFdGOUNUM3A2Vm0xQ1JuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVemJ6RnNUbUZaUm5WUFdGOUNUM3A2Vm0xQ1JuYxAB!2m1!1s0x808581f4a4ec2761:0xd5ec6486e9b5071"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxU1JrSjZjVFZNVW1aVE1HTmpWbEJ2U2twVlNsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Had a lovely time at this place. The service was amazing. We got there a bit early and they gave us a table at their bar next door while waiting, then brought us to the restaurant via the back door. They were attentive enough to notice I was wearing black pants, and gave me a black napkin as opposed to white to prevent lint from showing up.\n\nThe vibe was relaxed and quiet. The decor was eccentric with risqué paintings in Japanese style. It was edgy as if to signal that there would be surprises in the meal.\n\nThe meal was excellent. Many dishes were quite creative. All delicious! What I didn’t love was the lengthy explanation of each dish. While I understand the why, they took away from the experience because some felt like lectures.\n\nOverall, we had a great time here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Had a lovely time at this place. The service was amazing. We got there a bit early and they gave us a table at their bar next door while waiting, then brought us to the restaurant via the back door. They were attentive enough to notice I was wearing black pants, and gave me a black napkin as opposed to white to prevent lint from showing up.\n\nThe vibe was relaxed and quiet. The decor was eccentric with risqué paintings in Japanese style. It was edgy as if to signal that there would be surprises in the meal.\n\nThe meal was excellent. Many dishes were quite creative. All delicious! What I didn’t love was the lengthy explanation of each dish. While I understand the why, they took away from the experience because some felt like lectures.\n\nOverall, we had a great time here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Paul Cheong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107760199989401025038/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgocJrP5Pmq-aNmb0HfiBnD_7i6ADN9eq7k2cBQdOiMZAHfmLfcA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-19T13:33:45.010427184Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxU1JrSjZjVFZNVW1aVE1HTmpWbEJ2U2twVlNsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxU1JrSjZjVFZNVW1aVE1HTmpWbEJ2U2twVlNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x808581f4a4ec2761:0xd5ec6486e9b5071"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GTVdYSkNSMU53Ym5aMFVHZFlNVEkyZVRSeGVXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Ranking based on other mish 1s in the area. Food punches above it's weight! Everything was tasty, no complaints. Had their non alcoholic pairing which was phenomenal, one of the best I've had, it really elevated the food to the next level, which is rare for a non -alcohol. Plating was top notch, look at that dessert tree!  Slight markdown on service due to some delays and it took a while for beverages to arrive (after first dishes came out). Standouts: uni , unagi and Sando (see menu photo). Would go back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Ranking based on other mish 1s in the area. Food punches above it's weight! Everything was tasty, no complaints. Had their non alcoholic pairing which was phenomenal, one of the best I've had, it really elevated the food to the next level, which is rare for a non -alcohol. Plating was top notch, look at that dessert tree!  Slight markdown on service due to some delays and it took a while for beverages to arrive (after first dishes came out). Standouts: uni , unagi and Sando (see menu photo). Would go back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rai T", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105028329142497988492/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5SQbFl_HtxAlZFHuOtGxzooVLR1Dv_6QvIDIl7Q0Q22Y1hgZeGg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-13T10:57:25.210196430Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GTVdYSkNSMU53Ym5aMFVHZFlNVEkyZVRSeGVXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GTVdYSkNSMU53Ym5aMFVHZFlNVEkyZVRSeGVXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808581f4a4ec2761:0xd5ec6486e9b5071"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KbFZsVjJYM0J3TkMxeFdqSmxPVFJUTjBkVFpXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Came here for the Nisei and LURRA collab.\n\nA absolutely incredible experience, every dish was wonderful, the service was perfect.\n\nOnly downsides were\n1) It took four hours for our meal to complete which was a bit long\n2) There's only one washroom so there was a bit of a queue at times (but the staff were great about letting us know when it was available).\n\nWould highly recommend coming here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came here for the Nisei and LURRA collab.\n\nA absolutely incredible experience, every dish was wonderful, the service was perfect.\n\nOnly downsides were\n1) It took four hours for our meal to complete which was a bit long\n2) There's only one washroom so there was a bit of a queue at times (but the staff were great about letting us know when it was available).\n\nWould highly recommend coming here.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nicholas Pezarro", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116392824125118265998/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQUx3BmkIeWJEiU22dNCpoh9JXCaSD2AHiUND_nDEUr-AtJ-EnAA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-20T18:05:58.100387406Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KbFZsVjJYM0J3TkMxeFdqSmxPVFJUTjBkVFpXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KbFZsVjJYM0J3TkMxeFdqSmxPVFJUTjBkVFpXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808581f4a4ec2761:0xd5ec6486e9b5071"}, {"name": "places/ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOcFdGbE1WSGRYV1UxeFdGVjNTWFJxYTBSWlJrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "7 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Nisei, an intimate One Michelin-Starred restaurant in San Francisco. I got to experience their Winter 2025 - 13 course menu!\n\nThis is my second time coming here this year because I love the experience, service, and how the chefs make various different flavors come together cohesively, and the presentation speaks for itself.\n\nAs a photographer and creator, it is fun to have beautiful food be your muse. You will also leave here feeling satisfied and full by the end of your 13 course. And there's a story behind every dish, and all the ingredients are carefully sought out and used purposefully on each plate.\n\nUntil next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Nisei, an intimate One Michelin-Starred restaurant in San Francisco. I got to experience their Winter 2025 - 13 course menu!\n\nThis is my second time coming here this year because I love the experience, service, and how the chefs make various different flavors come together cohesively, and the presentation speaks for itself.\n\nAs a photographer and creator, it is fun to have beautiful food be your muse. You will also leave here feeling satisfied and full by the end of your 13 course. And there's a story behind every dish, and all the ingredients are carefully sought out and used purposefully on each plate.\n\nUntil next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jenn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116308399210131575773/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOJYCmKyfptRr1jU-e1B14QNGAAKFSydRe7q39VzLna4C0HMLGvg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-15T16:03:44.781544221Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOcFdGbE1WSGRYV1UxeFdGVjNTWFJxYTBSWlJrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOcFdGbE1WSGRYV1UxeFdGVjNTWFJxYTBSWlJrRRAB!2m1!1s0x808581f4a4ec2761:0xd5ec6486e9b5071"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJYSfspPSBhYARcVCbbkjGXg0/photos/AWCwydhpbRoCnpat_uN-s5PFYbuug0FcfNJuRKYSJycTFuKMu3m6e4Xg_idmluzRfChmvReyBeYpapA83VwCYLUTY1Z8nMtDA-9Hw0WnxSPCMUqSFEho54-VI4a_7vFMeFbqyR1ds0ph_JE_X2capTJxSJt-xSFka3XVYLxvoJKH66gwwjlPd1-lIuJv2fQnEc8qBFp-y75GU5QygD9ReiDOoxym59rvavylg4B-21YQgRnbI-5JdK25Ac28jvjQLyj1brWsfHS6u0AOSdWRDHMz_ppRIiUPa8E-UD3SfSTrw5_wTntoGGZr5QkGpwg3SR29rbpxpxzK160lBg-9p1pvYIND58SyrfUh83BvE19VuEo-52-TBTf4RMFy05FgBr5cXvKDfhynaf597hBe8pBncvAp8X_wUQh2FS8K_UDwY_LQWjw", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3199, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Nisei", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/107068210540461208381", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiUy6oM0ImKSNszH3umYKzZTrKcphH2UEjeBQJyX6yrl6btF3G=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDDwMD4ogE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDDwMD4ogE!2e10!